### 4. [CRITICAL] Authorization bypass through email modification
**Class:** other
**File:** `routes/orderHistory.ts:8-19`
**CVSS 3.1:** **9.9** (Critical) — `CVSS:3.1/AV:N/AC:L/PR:L/UI:N/S:C/C:H/I:H/A:H`
